    "text": "Let the Ivysaur and Bulbasaur go right now!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.513,
    "endTime": 17.934,
    "text": "Ha! How can we resist the pomp and circumstance of a sun-seeking mystery mob?"
  },
  {
